        <title>Activity: To describe and illustrate different cultures' ways of writing [LO 1.2]</title>
        <list id="id1170305899346" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Did you know?</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id8643347">The Mayas of Central America used numbers like these:</para>
