          <media id="id8119380_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics2-e7a2.png" id="id8119380__onlineimage" height="269" width="454"/>
          </media>
        </figure>
        <para id="id8115592">1. We have already looked at how the Romans wrote. Now look closely at the writing of the Maya Indians above and answer the following questions:</para>
