    <section id="id7480426">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id7760494"><emphasis>Learning Outcome 1: </emphasis>The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id8263338"><emphasis>Assessment Standard 1.2:</emphasis> We know this when the learner describes and illustrates various ways of writing numbers in different cultures (including local) throughout history.</para>
    </section>
